commit.message:
configure.ac: Don't run config-ml.in directly.

2007-10-14  H.J. Lu  <hongjiu.lu@intel.com>

	* configure.ac: Don't run config-ml.in directly.
	(multilib_arg): New.
	* configure: Regenerated.
